      "cell_type":"code",
      "input":"//define sql context\nval sqlContext = new org.apache.spark.sql.SQLContext(sparkContext)\n\n// createSchemaRDD is used to implicitly convert an RDD to a SchemaRDD.\nimport sqlContext.createSchemaRDD",
